* One tribe can conquere another
* Tribe can split in several parts if it has several leaders
* Food chain - who can eat whom
* Slave / master - slaves bring resources to master
* Different terrains - ground, water, road...
* Divide resources: inner - inside th creature, outer - belongs to the creature
* Houses
* Buy / sell resources
* Weapons (melee and shooting)
* Education
* Wars between tribes
* Friendship between tribes
* User interaction: control creature
* User interaction: modify terrain and processes (God mode)
* Jobs: work - get payed
* Trasports: private / public

